channel.title: God damit... this is pissing me off
channel.description: I just finished my second server, and now I want to have fun with global objects, but fed's global object tut won't work to other sources expect cheez and cheez doesn't work for me. Everytime I run the server it says something in the runserver and then won't let anyone in. Is there any other sources than cheez that the global objects tut works for?
